claim.claim-text:
1. An electroplating system for use in connection with a plurality of sources of additives, for electroplating semiconductor substrates, comprising: 
at least one electrolytic plating cell; 
an electrolyte reservoir; 
reservoir-cell fluid recirculation circuit means fluidically coupled to said reservoir and said cell, for recirculating electrolyte between said reservoir and said cell; 
dosing means coupled to said plurality of sources, for dosing electrolyte with said additives; and 
reservoir-dosing means fluid recirculation circuit means fluidically coupled to said reservoir and said dosing means, for recirculating electrolyte between said reservoir and said dosing means.
